WEBVTT

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:33.190
These days it seems like things
are happening very fast.

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:37.960
I don’t understand what status 
we will have in the history of our times.

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:42.080
This uncertainty and fear has us 
in it’s grasp to such an extent

00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:44.480
that we don’t think
about the future at all.

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:47.680
We don’t even try to meet it.

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:52.520
We ourselves see our future as a stranger
and think our tomorrow is a foreign place.

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:56.480
It is no foreign place.

00:01:56.480 --> 00:02:01.480
We ourselves, every moment, are creating
our own future, in front of our own eyes,